{"tid":2234091,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國出手?]VR可協助陳同佳自首有無得諗?","createTime":"2020-10-07T15:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:35:38.000Z","uid":213812,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8aaee6ae833fdfad317c600c7daa066f4014ee8","tid":2234091,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"Google總公司其實可唔可以幫幫呀佳仔，運用科技，用VR配上 Google Street view，帶個VR眼鏡，<a href=\"https://www.vive.com/tw/product/vive-pro-eye/overview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vive.com%2Ftw%2Fproduct%2Fvive-pro-eye%2Foverview%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=73835d90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vive.com/tw/product/vive-pro-eye/overview/</a> 而家市面上VIVE Pro Eyes算係唔錯嘅product, 咁呀管牧師就可以同佢遍走台灣．自首無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一站緊係警局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fER0x4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fER0x4.jpg&h=543510d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二站就係法院接受審訊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZfBsc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZfBsc9.jpg&h=c3b38bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三站台灣最高度設防監獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />綠島監獄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNt7yTc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNt7yTc.jpg&h=8cab6063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講咁多 !緊係同管牧師飲返杯珍珠奶茶先啦屌 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佳仔: 管牧師, 因上帝之名, Cheers!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77TvwHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77TvwHc.jpg&h=e7fed0be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9819e800c6ad7c803ef03ca85f01bbba77ce702a","tid":2234091,"uid":213812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"佳佳: 牧師牧師, 我而家係西門町呀, 訂咗馬辣鴛鴦火鍋兩位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/3gGEAyzxfqAYPWdLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F3gGEAyzxfqAYPWdLA&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=a4ae6476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/3gGEAyzxfqAYPWdLA</a>"},{"pid":"4a33b3f0d5203d3aeecf9a82e5b4a3aa6fe8bac1","tid":2234091,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23827f51edac4ce9be1ef9e9ac5d72d8f04d512d","tid":2234091,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0880bfed4abf2b6c0b22a02d658df7cfb7fc9805","tid":2234091,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"佳佳"},{"pid":"8512dc152475e0b6f213e3b1e11df7b8486ab2cc","tid":2234091,"uid":81505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T15:26:29.000Z","msg"